Cell C CEO Reichelt Quits, Chairman Takes Role Until Appointment is Made

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-13T09:56:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-13/cell-c-ceo-reichelt-quits-chairman-takes-role-until-appointment-is-made.html
Cell C (Pty) Ltd., a South African
mobile-phone company, said Chief Executive Officer Lars P.
Reichelt will leave the company today for personal reasons.  He will be replaced by Chairman Simon Duffy until a
replacement is appointed, Johannesburg-based Cell C said an e-
mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  